content.text: Access one-on-one mentorship from experienced professionals who can help guide your project from concept to completion. Mentors are available throughout the event to provide advice, technical support, and feedback, ensuring you make the most of your hackathon experience.

Whether you’re an in-person attendee or considering joining virtually, JSC Hack 2024 offers flexibility to fit your needs.
We highly encourage on-site participation for the full experience, allowing you to immerse yourself in all aspects of the event.

By attending in person, you'll have the opportunity to access mentorship from industry experts, recharge in our relaxation zones, and participate in engaging workshops & panels.

Additionally, our event is designed to foster team collaboration, ensuring you can work effectively with others whether you're on-site or virtual. For those who prefer to join remotely, hybrid options are available to ensure you don’t miss out on these valuable experiences.

Step away from the hustle and recharge in our relaxation zones. These areas are equipped with comfortable seating, quiet spaces, and ambient lighting to help you unwind and refocus. It’s the perfect place to take a break, meditate, or even grab a quick nap.

Engage with industry leaders through a variety of workshops and panels. These sessions will cover topics from cutting-edge technology to the latest trends in space exploration. Whether you’re a beginner or an expert, there’s something for everyone to learn and take away.

Whether you’re joining with a team or looking to form one, the Team Collaboration option provides a platform to connect with other participants. Use our matchmaking tools to find like-minded individuals or join an existing team to tackle challenges together. Benefit from shared expertise and collective creativity.
